                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/698" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0089</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10670 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">伊泰煤炭股份公司的融资决策方案如何制定</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How to write on YiTai coal company&#39;s risk analysis report</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">颉茂华</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">伊泰煤炭公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">矿冶业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">融资条件；融资理论；方案；决策；2012百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Financing conditions; finance theory; programs; decision-making</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">自2000年以来，中国煤炭工业经历一个快速发展时期，无论是产业规模还是效益都发生了翻天覆地的变化。从2005年到2007年国家连续颁布了一系列政策，提高了行业进入门槛，以整合为主、新建为辅，限制小煤矿建设，发展大中型煤矿。随之煤炭产业整合调整拉开序幕。竞争格局演绎为各大企业集团之间的强强竞争。为了适应环境，伊泰煤炭股份公司制定了集中在相关多元化方面的发展战略，并准备在2012年制定新的融资规划。2011年2月18日，伊泰煤炭公司完成了2010年报。董事会召开会议，要求融资规划部就公司目前的财务状况（主要是基于报表）提交一份融资规划报告，以配合公司发展战略规划，确立科学的理财计划。融资规划部长张XX及其全体成员根据公司2010年报，经过一个多月的准备，于2011年4月30日召开了一次“伊泰煤炭股份公司融资规划方案”决策讨论会。本案例是这次会议争论的几个主要融资方案。通过对该案例分析可以熟悉如何利用相关理论对企业融资进行科学性规划与决策。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since 2000, China&#39;s coal industry has experienced rapid development, both the size of the industry and the efficiency of the enterprises have undergone enormous changes. From 2005 to 2007, the state has promulgated a series of policies so as to improve the industry&#39;s barriers to entry. The purpose of the policy is to integrate the coal industry ,slow down the speed of setting up new enterprises, limit the building of small coal mines, develop the large and median-sized mines. And the consolidation of the coal industry came as a result. However, the competition patten has changed to the fierce competition among the huge enterprises. In order to adapt to the environment, YiTai coal stock company formulated diversifying development strategies, so as to adapt to the changing environment, and also planned to set new financing planning. On February 18 2011, YiTai coal Company completed the Annual Report of 2010. The board held a meeting to request the financial sector submit a risk analysis report on account of the company&#39;s current risk, to meet the requirement of the company&#39;s development strategy, to establish a scientific financial planning. Mr Zhang ,the dean of the Financial Planning Sector , held a forum called &quot;YiTai Coal Corporation financial planning &quot; on April 30th,2011.The forum provided the background for our case study. The main goal of our case study is being familiar with the application of the scientific enterprise risk analysis theory.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2010</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司理财》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">融资战略与决策</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2011-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
